data.description: Stunning and modern this ONE story home built in 2016 by LGI Homes! Boasts a single-story design that offers three bedrooms and two bathrooms. The kitchen has stunning wood cabinets and an open floor plan to the living/dining areas. As you step inside the home's entryway, you'll be greeted by a spacious living area with no carpeting to detract from the beauty of your surroundings. The large master closet provides ample storage space for all your wardrobe essentials while the utility room makes laundry day effortless. Enjoy sipping on your morning coffee or diving into a good book in complete comfort thanks to the covered deck/patio that overlooks lush greenery. Recently updated for easy access and modern convenience, the master bathroom shower is unlike those you've seen in this floor plan! Owner updated the tub/shower combo to walk-in shower! Water softener is negotiable as well so you can enjoy pristine water quality throughout your home. This truly exceptional property is one not to be missed!
